  <name>Eyedropper</name>
  <summary>Eyedropper applet for cosmic desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Pick colors from anywhere on your screen with the COSMIC Eyedropper applet.
      Click the eyedropper icon in the panel, then click on any pixel to capture
      its color. The selected color can be copied in multiple formats including
      HEX, RGB, and HSL.
    </p>
  </description>
  <icon type="stock">io.github.nalladev.CosmicExtAppletEyedropper</icon>
  <url type="vcs-browser">https://github.com/nalladev/cosmic-ext-applet-eyedropper</url>
